title: India, Marshall Islands sign MoU on development projects
description: NEW DELHI: India on Monday signed an agreement with the Marshall Islands to provide an annual grant for four community development projects as part of New Delhi’s outreach to Pacific Island states. title: Unemployment rate at 3.2%, will come down below 3% in future: Mansukh Mandaviya
